<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Admin — Dashboard</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <style>
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body {
        font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
        min-height: 100svh;
        background: #0f172a;
        color: #f1f5f9;
      }
      header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #1e293b;
        background: #0f172a;
      }
      header h1 { font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 600; }
      a.logout {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: #94a3b8;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      a.logout:hover { color: #f1f5f9; }
      main {
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .welcome {
        background: #1e293b;
        border: 1px solid #334155;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      }
      .welcome h2 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      .welcome p { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #94a3b8; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Admin</h1>
      <a class="logout" href="/admin/logout">Sair</a>
    </header>
    <main>
      <div class="welcome">
        <h2>Dashboard</h2>
        <p>Bem-vinda, Isabella. Em breve você poderá gerenciar os comentários do site aqui.</p>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
